body: "## Agent need\npm must be a universal PM tool: every project has its own vocabulary, so an agent must reshape types/statuses/fields/workflows through config rather than code.\n\n## Delivered surface (pm-8jdc)\ncore/schema (types, statuses, fields, workflows, presets, inference); core/config nested-settings + positional-value; core/profile presets/plan/describe/lint; pm init --type-preset.\n\n## Verified by\nschema-customization integration and profile-lint tests. Enduring agent-value statement for the customization capability; new work lands in pm-8jdc."
